        <abstract> 
<p>Discusses his work [<hi rend="italic">Flora fossilis Arctica</hi>, vol. 4, pt 1 (1876)].</p>  
<p>Sends copy of [<hi rend="italic">Fossile Pflanzen von Sumatra</hi> (1874)]. Comments on climate in Tertiary period, especially on Sumatra.</p> 
            <p>Comments on theory of Thomas Belt concerning climatic change in ice age.</p>
        </abstract>
